  <Faq>
    <FaqItem question="Can I help with Flüüfff?">
      <p>Of course! You can contact us through the contact form and we’ll look into it.</p>
      <p>But the best way to support Flüüfff is simply by attending and spreading the word.</p>
    </FaqItem>
    {
      /*<FaqItem question="Are there rules during the convention?" />
    <FaqItem question="Where can I find the websites of previous editions?" /> */
    }
    <FaqItem question="Do I need to be 18 or older to attend?">
      <p>Yes. Flüüfff is an 18+ event, even if some parts are family-friendly in nature.</p>
      <p>This is for legal, insurance, and community safety reasons.</p>
      <p>All attendees must be 18 or older at the start of the convention — no exceptions.</p>
    </FaqItem>
    <FaqItem question="What if I don't know anyone?">
      <p>
        That’s completely okay. Flüüfff is full of friendly faces, quiet corners, and fun things to do. Many people come
        solo and leave with new connections.
      </p>
    </FaqItem>
    <FaqItem question="How do I find out what's happening during the convention?">
      <p>
        You'll receive a conbook which includes a printed schedule. You'll also be able to find this schedule on our
        website when it is published!
      </p>
      <p>Our team will also post updates on site and via our Telegram channels.</p>
    </FaqItem>
  </Faq>
